trsp:ttram:AF19-01
  a skos:Concept ;
  skos:prefLabel "Business Continuity Plan"@en ;
  skos:description "Ensuring business continuity by maintaining normal operations and preparing for disruptions. This includes non-technical processes (for technical, see AF29 “Technical Infrastructure”) related to the organisation, digital object management (see AF09 \"Workflows\"), and security (see AF30 \"Security\"). It also covers recovery plans for events like service interruptions and disasters. Continuity includes succession planning for the end of a service."@en ;
